  "name": "ATX Disco Cruise",
  "description": "Join the BEST party on Lake Travis! Austin's exclusive ATX Disco Cruise features professional DJ entertainment, professional photographer, disco dance floor, giant floats, and incredible party atmosphere. Perfect for bachelor and bachelorette parties celebrating together. Every disco cruise includes professional entertainment, photo delivery, party supplies, and an unforgettable experience with multiple groups celebrating together. BYOB friendly with full cooler service. Three time slots available with different pricing to fit your schedule and budget. Operating Fridays 12-4 PM and Saturdays 11-3 PM or 3:30-7:30 PM from March to October. America's only multi-group bachelor/bachelorette party cruise experience. What's Included on Every Cruise: Professional DJ playing favorites ALL DAY, professional photographer for epic moments, digital photo delivery 2-3 weeks after cruise, giant unicorn floats and lily pads, party supplies including cups, koozies and decorations, ice water stations throughout cruise, clean restroom facilities on board, plenty of shaded lounge areas, and multi-group energy and party atmosphere that creates an unforgettable celebration experience.",
